11 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Transfer of funds. By June 30, 2025, the state treasurer shall transfer
12 $14 million from the general fund to the fund established pursuant to 17-6-203(8) and [section 1 of this act] for
13 the construction of additional workforce housing in Deer Lodge, Montana.
